; 生きていた他のメンバーの発言
[iscript]
for(var i = 0; i < game.party.members.count; i++)
{
	var one = game.party.members[i];
	if(! one.active || one == o.テオ) continue;
	game.curChara = one;
	break;
}
[endscript]
[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh057 f=05]「Captain, for now, we should carry the three of them to a church!」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd057 f=05]「Captain, for now, we should carry the three of them to a church!」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg047 f=05]「Captain, for now, we should carry the three of them to a church!」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve058 f=05]「Captain, we need to get the three of them to a church!」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs059 f=05]「Captain, we need to get the three of them to a church!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=12]「Yes, let's hurry!」[k]
We can resurrect the three of them now. Let's quickly transport everyone to a church.[k]
Currently, our forces are down significantly. If we are attacked by the enemy again, we are in danger of being wiped out. We must get to a safe place as soon as possible...[k]
We were told that the underground town is on [b]B5[/b]. Since we're so close to the town, it might be safer to continue onward than to return to the surface from here.[k]
