;◇イベント04・地下の町ライムストーンに到達
*return_4

; ☆フリーモード
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*return_4 cond='game.isFreeMode'

; 地下の町ライムストーン
@saveon
@wait time=1000
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=05]「This is the underground city...!」[k]
Passing through the narrow passageway that was the town gate, I found a huge cavern beyond, and to my surprise, a town where people lived had been built there.[k]
It's unbelievable that people live in places so deep underground...[k]
[少女 f=priest_green_00]「Ah, brave adventurer. Welcome to our town!」[k]
[少女 f=priest_green_00]「Thank you very much for your help in helping me. As promised, I am pleased to present you all with a gift of thanks.」[k]
[textoff]
@getitem item=特効薬
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=02]「Thank you.」[k]
[少女 f=priest_green_00]「There are many unusual things in this underground town that aren't found above ground. Please take your time to look around.」[k]
The girl left, bowing repeatedly.[k]
[if exp='game.party.hasPatient(o.死亡) || game.party.hasPatient(o.灰)']
	[テオ f=06]「Now, first we have to resurrect the dead members...」[k]
	[textoff]
	@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()'
	@se f=up1
	@notice text="<y>All deceased members were resurrected at the temple!"
	[texton]
[endif]
[テオ f=06]「Everyone is tired. For now, let's spend the night at this underground town's inn.」[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@wait time=1000

; 夜・ライムストーンの宿屋
@bg f=0001
@mu f=worry
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Murmur is back...[k]
I thought we'd beaten her, so I never thought I would have to fight her again. To be honest, I am very shocked. Especially since she was such a troublesome enemy.[k]
What was even more devastating was that my demon hunting power was taken away from me.[k]
The loss of it means that next time we encounter Murmur, we are finished.[k]
This time she was out of shape, which saved my life, but that won't happen next time. She will unleash her fatal breath and we will all die.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I realized that our situation was now hopeless.[k]
From now on, we can only continue our adventure, praying that we don't encounter Murmur.[k]
But how is that possible? She said she'd be back to kill us. I don't think that cunning devil will let us off the hook so easily.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Now that this has happened, we must once again turn to the power of the god Polaris, but it will still take some time to collect all the remaining magic stones.[k]
There is no way to protect ourselves, so the party is in danger.[k]
We may no longer have any choice but to disband the party and quit the adventure...[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@wait time=1000

; 翌朝・宿屋のロビー
@bg f=0003 b
@fgf c=テオ f=06
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「Everyone, before we leave, listen to what I have to say!」[k]
Before I left, I decided to gather everyone in the party and talk about my thoughts from last night.[k]
Everyone became gloomy after hearing it.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...So, I am considering disbanding the party. Let me know what you guys think.」[k]
Well, what will they all say...?[k]

@mu f=brave

[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh058 f=07]「I don't want that!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve059 f=07]「I cannot accept that!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd058 f=51]「No, we can't～!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg048 f=08]「That's... no way...!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs060 f=07]「Absolutely not! No way!」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「[キャラ]...!」[k]

[   if exp='SYL2'][マルエット２ v=vs061 f=07]「That's a terrible idea! Of course I want to continue adventuring with everyone!」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO2'][ミューズ２ v=vg049 f=08]「I don't like it either...! I want to continue adventuring with everyone...!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA2'][フレデリカ２ v=vd059 f=51]「I don't like it either! Of course I want to continue my adventures with everyone～!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF2'][クレア２ v=ve060 f=07]「I also can't accept it! I definitely want to continue adventuring with everyone!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM2'][リム２ v=vh059 f=07]「Don't do it! I want to continue my adventures with everyone!」[k]
[endif]

[マックス f=05]「That's right, [テオ]. It's not like you to suddenly say something like that.」[k]
[ライナス f=06]「I'm against it too... I'd be in trouble if I lost my livelihood...」[k]
The members unanimously oppose the dissolution.[k]
[テオ f=06]「However, there is a definite risk of total annihilation by Murmur. Once her power is restored, there is no guarantee that we'll be safe.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「We can think about that later.」[k]
[マックス f=01]「It'll take some time for her to recover her strength, right? So there's no need to rush into a decision to disband now, is there?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
@fg c=テオ f=02
[テオ f=02]「...Well, that's true. Okay, I'll wait a little longer before making a decision.」[k]
[name n=Members]「... (Phew)」[k]
[マックス f=03]「All right! Now that we've decided, let's go find some work for today! Let's gather information on magic stones too!」[k]
When they heard my announcement, everyone looked relieved. For now, it seems that we won't have to disband.[k]
...However, my concerns remain unresolved. The fact remains that the devil will eventually come to deliver us our final blow.[k]
If all the magic stones are collected by then, it will be possible to borrow the power of the god Polaris, but that is not realistic.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
We need to seriously consider new measures to protect everyone while we still can...[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@addevent map=ヤネクの森・霧の谷 num=5
@eval exp='game.party.recovery()'
@eval exp='game.elapseByStaying()'
@eval exp='game.hotelView.checkLevelUp()'
[waittrig name="finishLevelUpInEvent"]
@fa
@w05
[townoff]




;■ブルー加入

;◇イベント01・宝物庫の近くに行く
*treasury_1

; 地下迷宮・宝物庫の近く
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「This is...!」[k]
Deep inside the cave were the ruins of a stone structure. It looked old but very sturdy.[k]
[マックス f=01]「Hey, isn't this the treasure vault we heard about?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Probably...」[k]
The client's instructions were to bring back three artifacts from here. However, this place is a treasure trove of items that once belonged to royalty. There are likely many other valuable items here as well.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[マックス f=01]「What's up, [テオ]? Is there something bothering you?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「No... not really...」[k]
I'm sure I've had a request like this before... I have a bad feeling about this...[k]
[マックス f=01]「Let's find the entrance first, [テオ]!」[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント02・宝物庫の扉の前でブルーたちに出会う
*treasury_2

; 宝物庫の扉の前
@fg l=ブルー f=08 b
@fg r=サンドラ f=05
@mu f=anxiety
[texton w=1]
[サンドラ v=vn004 f=05]「Oh...」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「Oh. It's you...!」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Ugh!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「B-Blue...!」[k]
To my surprise, Blue was right in front of the entrance.[k]
He and the elf he had with him before had come to this ruin together.[k]
Their objective is likely the same as ours; the treasure from the quest.[k]
[ブルー f=08]「...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Blue...」[k]
Tension and hostility runs high between us.[k]
From Blue's perspective, our party is one of the few opponents who have defeated him. What's more, the leader of that party is someone he once treated like a subordinate and looked down on, so his anger is even greater.[k]
On the other hand, for me, Blue is someone I'll forever bear a grudge against, and at the same time, someone who instinctively inspires fear.[k]
Even though we defeated him once, Blue is still a formidable opponent, and I can't say I've overcome my fear of him yet.[k]
If Blue decides to do so, we could face retaliation at any time. It's difficult to remain calm when faced with such an opponent.[k]
[ブルー f=08]「...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[マックス f=12]「H-hey, what should we do...?」[k]
Blue and I continue to stare each other down.[k]
Along with hostility, there is a sense of mutual suspicion, as if we're each trying to figure out what the other is thinking.[k]
@cl b
@fg c=サンドラ f=53
@st
[サンドラ v=vn005 f=53]「Okay, okay, both of you, stop it now.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Aaa...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...What, Sandra?」[k]
Sandra broke the tension with a lighthearted voice, clapping her hands.[k]
@mu f=cave
[サンドラ v=vn006 f=55]「There's no point in glaring at each other. Let's just complete the quest. We have the same goal, right?」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Y-yes...」[k]
Sandra scolded us, and I remembered my original purpose.[k]
Let's put Blue aside for now. Right now, we need to enter the treasure vault and complete the request...[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
At the entrance, there is a stone door that looks very sturdy. How can it be opened?[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=02
[サンドラ v=vn007 f=02]「...This is a structure that opens when you chant a few ancient words.」[k]
[マックス f=51]「Oh! You understand! Sandra, you're amazing!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn008 f=01]「It's not an uncommon mechanism in ancient buildings. The ancient language used in the chant is simple, so it's not that difficult.」[k]
Sandra replied calmly. She seemed to have figured out the secret of the door at a glance.[k]
If it had been just our group here, we would have been stuck in front of this door. So I'm rather grateful.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn009 f=01]「Well, I'll open it then.」[k]
@cl
Sandra stands in front of the door and chants some spell-like words. Then...[k]
[textoff]

; 石の扉が開く
@wait time=500
@playse storage=tremble
@quake time=3000 hmax=5 vmax=0
@wait time=500
[texton]
∗rrrrumble∗[auto time=1000]
[textoff]
@stopquake
