[texton]
With a deep rumbling sound, the stone door swung open with force.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Wow! It's open!」[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=01
[サンドラ v=vn010 f=01]「Well then, let's go inside.」[k]
[textoff]
