; 宝物庫内
@saveon
[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...?」[k]
We went inside the treasure chamber, but it was empty and there was nothing inside. There were no treasures to be found.[k]
[ブルー f=08]「Huh? Where's the treasure?」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Hey, it's empty!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn011 f=05]「What do you mean, nothing? What on earth...」[k]
Everyone seems irate and confused.[k]
According to the quest, this place was supposed to be overflowing with treasure. However, no matter how much I look around the vault, I can't see any at all.[k]
What on earth is going on? Could it be that this isn't the place we were looking for?[k]
[？？？]「Hahahaha! You foolish adventurers!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, someone behind me laughed mockingly![k]
[テオ f=07]「Who's that?」[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk turn=n
@wait time=500
[texton]
We immediately turn around and prepare our weapons. Then...[k]
[textoff]
@se f=roar
@fg c=demon_white left=450 top=-232
@wait time=500
@mu f=satan
[texton w=1]
[マックス f=11]「Eek!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn012 f=09]「H-hey, what is that?!」[k]
Behind us was something huge, shaped like a human with large wings.[k]
[テオ f=10]「A... demon?」[k]
[？？？ f=demon_00]「Kukukuku...」[k]
It certainly looked like a demon. However, compared to a typical one, its body was clearly one or two sizes larger.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Could it be a high-ranking demon...?」[k]
[？？？ f=demon_00]「That's right. I'm Malphas.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn013 f=12]「M-Malphas...?!」[k]
Sandra shouted this with a frightened expression, her body shaking.[k]
No wonder. If what he said was true, then this place must be home to a high-ranking demon that most people have never seen before.[k]
Malphas. A high-ranking demon on par with Murmur. Why are such high-ranking demons coming to the human realm one after another...?![k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「Hah... You foolish human adventurers.」[k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「That request was made by me to lure you all here! To consume the physical strength and magical power of you adventurers and fully restore my own power!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn014 f=11]「W-what did you say...?」[k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「...Hmm, everyone has decent magical powers. This should be interesting. Hehhehheh.」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Hey, wait a minute! This is no joke! I'm not going to let you eat me!」[k]
[ブルー f=07]「Hey! You lot! Let's fight this guy!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I know that without being told!」[k]
This is an emergency. We must work together with Blue and Sandra to defeat this demon.[k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「Hahaha...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, the demon Malphas clasped his hands together in front of his chest and made a sign. That stance was definitely...[k]
[ブルー f=08]「W-what's it doing?」[k]
[テオ f=11]「Everyone, be careful! She's about to unleash a fatal breath attack!」[k]
[マックス f=11]「W-what?!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn015 f=11]「What do you mean, "fatal breath"?」[k]
[テオ f=11]「If it hits us, we'll all die in an instant! We have to escape immediately or we'll be wiped out!」[k]
I used to be able to block the fatal breath because I had the power to exorcise demons. However, now that I've lost that power, I have no way to defend myself against their attacks.[k]
[ブルー f=07]「What?! Is that true?!」[k]
[テオ f=11]「Everyone, run away quickly! Otherwise...」[k]

