[テオ f=12]「...!」[k]
I witnessed an unbelievable scene.[k]
I couldn't believe it. Blue activated the power of exorcism![k]
[name n=Malphas f=demon_00]「Why? Why isn't my fatal breath working?」[k]
Malphas, whose fatal breath had been blocked, was completely shaken. He must have thought he could win for sure...[k]
