[texton]
Somehow, we managed to defeat the devil Malphas. For a moment, I thought it was all over.[k]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=06
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
...Without Blue's power, we would not have been able to win this battle. In fact, we would have been completely wiped out.[k]
Blue saving us is something that gives me very mixed feelings, but I have to admit it.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Blue...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...What.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Well... thank you. You saved us.」[k]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=01
[ブルー f=01]「...Why do you need to thank me? Don't do anything unnecessary.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn018 f=09]「Come on, Blue. Just be honest.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「...Hmph. Let's go, Sandra.」[k]
@cl
Blue urges Sandra to leave.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Wait, Blue! Just tell me one thing!」[k]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=06
[ブルー f=06]「...What?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Are you a demon hunter?!」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「...Demon hunter?」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「I don't know anything about that.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
He clearly has the ability though. Does that mean he isn't aware of it himself?[k]
[テオ f=05]「Did you know about your power to exorcise demons?」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...I don't know about that either.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「You don't know... Then what about that power from earlier...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「I don't know. It just happened.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
So, does that mean Blue was unknowingly a demon hunter?[k]
[ブルー f=05]「That's enough. Sandra, let's go.」[k]
@cl
[サンドラ v=vn019 f=55]「Wait, Blue!」[k]
Leaving me standing there in shock, Blue and Sandra quickly walked away.[k]
