[texton]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
From what he said, Blue really seemed to know nothing about it.[k]
In other words, he is unknowingly a demon hunter.[k]
I don't know the details, but Blue also has the ability to hunt demons, and when he faced off against Malphas earlier, that power was activated. Just like when I unexpectedly manifested my power during my battle with Murmur.[k]
Blue probably has demon-hunting blood running through his veins too... We may even be distant relatives or something. [k]
The demon-hunting family line began about 400 years ago with a founding figure, and the power has been passed down to their descendants from generation to generation.[k]
However, there are families with strong bloodlines and those without. Not many of those families can fight demons in actual combat by activating exorcism powers. My father was one of the few descendants of such a family.[k]
However, not all descendants' family trees have been traced, and it cannot be denied that some bloodlines have been lost to history.[k]
...Blue was among them. That possibility is quite likely.[k]
At the very least, the exorcism power he unleashed was real. That much is certain.[k]
[textoff]
