; 宝物庫内
[texton]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「Eeeek, demon, you won't find me tasty even if you eat me!」[k]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「Huh...? I thought it was a demon, but it's a human...? Where did that demon go?」[k]
We told the old man that we had defeated the demon.[k]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「What! Is that so... I'm sorry. Thanks to you, I was saved.」[k]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「I am a resident of Limestone Town. I accepted a quest posted in town and came here to search for treasure.」[k]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「However, no matter how much I searched, I couldn't find the treasure. That's when I saw that terrifying demon. I've been hiding so that it wouldn't find me.」[k]
[if exp='! game.isFreeMode']
	[テオ f=05]「Is that so... As for the treasure, it seems that it was all a lie made up by the demon. So, no matter how much you search, you won't find any treasure.」[k]
[else]
	We told the old man that the story of the treasure was a lie made up by the demon.[k]
[endif]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「I see... Well, that was a waste of time. Oh well, I guess I'll head back to town.」[k]
[name n="Old Man" f=waroth_00]「Oh, by the way, I actually run a magic shop in Limestone Town. You're an adventurer, are you not? If you'd like, please come visit my shop. I'm sure it will be useful to you.」[k]
[name n=Hawkwaros f=waroth_00]「My name is Hawkwaros. Nice to meet you. Well, I'll be off now.」[k]
[textoff]
