[texton]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Blue has the power to hunt demons...[k]
We managed to defeat Malphas, the demon we encountered today, but Murmur is still out there somewhere.[k]
Her goal is to overturn this world. We must stop her at all costs. We cannot ignore her actions.[k]
But I don't have the power to exorcise demons right now.[k]
Last time, thanks to Murmur's strength not being fully recovered, we managed to get away with it.[k]
However, it is unclear what will happen next. If I encounter her again, she may wipe out the party with her fatal breath.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
The power to exorcise demons is indeed necessary. As long as Murmur exists somewhere in this world, it is absolutely essential to have a means of protecting oneself from the Breath of Death.[k]
As the leader of the party, I have to protect all the members. Knowing the threat, we simply can't afford not to take countermeasures. [k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I didn't want to make this choice if I could help it. I have my pride too. I don't want to bow down to a man like that.[k]
But I have no choice but to rely on him.[k]
