[texton]
[ブルー f=08]「...!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn020 f=01]「Oh, good morning.」[k]
As we were leaving the inn with everyone, we ran into Blue and Sandra.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn021 f=01]「You guys stayed here too, huh? We're heading back to the surface, so would you like to come with us?」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Hey, ignore them. Let's go, Sandra.」[k]
@cl l
[サンドラ v=vn022 f=55]「Ah, wait a minute, Blue.」[k]
@cl r
Blue tries to quickly leave with Sandra.[k]
[テオ f=11]「Wait! Blue!」[k]
I hurriedly called out to Blue. I couldn't let him leave like that.[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=08
[ブルー f=08]「What the hell do you want?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Well... I have a favor to ask you...」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「A... favor...?」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「Why should I listen to your request? This is ridiculous. I'm leaving.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn023 f=11]「Wait a minute, Blue.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Come on, let's go, Sandra.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn024 f=09]「You don't have to be so rude. Why don't you at least listen to what he has to say?」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「...Tch.」[k]
Sandra managed to keep Blue there. We couldn't miss this opportunity.[k]
[テオ f=05]「This is important. Listen to me, Blue.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Yesterday, the power you unleashed is called the power of exorcism, and it's a very precious thing.」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=06
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「It is a rare and valuable ability that can defend against the fatal breath used by some demons. Very few possess this ability.」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...So?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I'm currently fighting a high-ranking demon named Murmur. She's the true identity of Miredy, who was in your party a while ago.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn025 f=11]「Miredy?! She was a high-ranking demon?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Miredy, or rather Murmur, is plotting to overturn this world.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Once I discovered this, I had to take action. That's why I've been fighting Murmur until today.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Murmur is also a very dangerous demon who uses what she calls<r>"Breath of Death". However, I had the power to exorcise demons, just like you. That's why I've been able to fight until now.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...Unfortunately, for some reason, my demon hunting powers have been lost.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Fighting Murmur in my current state would lead to the destruction of the entire party. Therefore, in order to protect my precious allies, I have no choice but to give up the fight against Murmur.」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「However, if we leave her alone, this world will be in danger. If we're not careful, everyone who lives here may end up being ruled by demons. In other words, someone has to fight Murmur.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...No one else but you has that power right now. Please, Blue. Will you fight that demon for me?」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=08
[ブルー f=08]「Huh? Why me?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「As far as I know, you are the only one with the power to exorcise demons.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「You're the only one who can fight that demon! Please, fight! The future of this world depends on it!」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=05
[ブルー f=05]「Hmph, who cares? It's none of my business.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn026 f=55]「That isn't true. If what he says is correct, then all of us are in trouble.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Shut up. I don't care! I'm not a champion of justice or anything like that. I don't care what happens to the world.」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「I do whatever I want. All that matters is whether I feel good or not.」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=01
[ブルー f=01]「The world turning upside down? That's fine with me. It will be more interesting if there are demons roaming around everywhere!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn027 f=09]「Hey, what are you talking about, Blue...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...Sure, for a tough guy like you, it might not be a big deal. But for most people, it's a matter of life and death.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I can't just stand by and do nothing. After all, I was born into a family of demon hunters. Just like my father did, I want to protect people from the clutches of demons.」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=54
[ブルー f=54]「...」[k]
Blue doesn't respond.[k]
...I knew it. There was no way he would accept my request. Considering his personality, it would be extremely difficult to persuade him.[k]
But I can't back down. The fate of the world hangs in the balance in these negotiations![k]
[テオ f=06]「...Then let's do this. Blue, come with our party.」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=08
[ブルー f=08]「What?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「You don't have to do anything. Just follow behind us. Can't you do that much?」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=06
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「As long as you stand behind me, that's enough to protect everyone from a demon's deadly breath.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「All you have to do is watch us fight. Okay? At least do that much for us!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I've thought about it a lot, but we have no choice but to rely on you!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「I'll pay you properly! Please, Blue, listen to my plea! I want to protect my friends at all costs!」[k]
I bow my head desperately. It's really frustrating to bow my head to someone I hate, but I have no choice.[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=19
[ブルー f=19]「...No way. I'm not going to bother with such a hassle.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Blue...」[k]
Despite my feelings, Blue remained adamantly opposed. No matter how hard I tried to appease him, he wouldn't budge.[k]
Damn it... what should I do...?![k]
[サンドラ v=vn028 f=09]「Isn't it fine to do that much? You can't just ignore Miredy's misdeeds, can you?」[k]
[ブルー f=19]「It's like I said. It's none of my business. I don't care what happens to other people.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn029 f=09]「After we lost, everyone left the party, and it's been tough finding work and making money, hasn't it? 」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=08
[ブルー f=08]「...」[k]
[マックス f=52]「...Pfft, seriously? ♪」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn030 f=01]「This is a good offer. Why not go for it?」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「Shut up! Why do I have to obey this guy?」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn031 f=09]「Come on... You're just being stubborn...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
If I can offer Blue some kind of benefit, he might agree to my request. Something new, other than money.[k]
[ブルー f=05]「If you go on a journey, you can't eat whenever you want, and there's few women around to play with.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn032 f=09]「What do you mean? If you want someone to keep you company at night, I'm right here!」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=01
