[ブルー f=01]「Your party has some pretty good-looking women, so if I can sleep with them freely, I'll go along with it. With Sandra joining in, I'm sure I won't get bored at night.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn034 f=09]「Well... what do you need those kids for? I can satisfy you on my own...」[k]

[if exp='HUM'][リム f=28]「...」[k][endif]
[if exp='ELF'][クレア f=28]「...」[k][endif]
[if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ f=28]「...」[k][endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ f=28]「...」[k][endif]
[if exp='SYL'][マルエット f=28]「...」[k][endif]

Everyone in the party fell silent, looking nervous.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「If you don't like that, find another woman. Just make sure I always have a woman. That's the condition.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
Asking everyone in the party to provide sexual services... I can't accept such conditions.[k]
[テオ f=12]「...Hey, Blue. There must be some other way...」[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=51
[ブルー f=51]「I won't accept anything else. If you don't agree, I won't accompany your party, or fight that devil.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
What a despicable man...! Taking advantage of our weakness and demanding sexual favors...![k]
Once again, I feel sickened by Blue's humanity. This man really doesn't care if he tramples on other people.[k]
I can't accept such a terrible request. But if I can't get Blue to join us here, the moment we encounter Murmur, we're done for.[k]
I want to continue adventuring with everyone. If I quit now, all my hard work until now may have been for nothing.[k]
However... I can't ask my friends to sacrifice their bodies for that...[k]
Is this where our adventure ends...?[k]
@fg c=ブルー f=02
[ブルー f=02]「You won't do it? Then forget it. Bye, I'm going home.」[k]
@cl
With that, Blue starts to leave.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Ah...!」[k]
Damn it...! It's no good after all...! Is it over already...?![k]
