[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh064 f=35]「I'm fine with that, Captain. More than anything, I want to continue my adventure with everyone.」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve065 f=35]「I can accept it too. I want to continue adventuring with everyone.」[k]
[elsif exp='isDWA'][フレデリカ v=vd064 f=35]「Oh, I'm fine too! I want to continue my adventures with everyone!」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg053 f=35]「I'm fine too... It's more important to continue the adventure with everyone...」[k]
