The party members declare that they will accept Blue's proposal one after another.[k]
[if exp='game.party.members.count >= 5']
	@eval exp='game.curChara = game.party.members[f.heroineNumbers[2]]'
	[テオ f=12]「Um... What about everyone else...?」[k]
	[キャラ f=08]「... ∗nod∗」[k]
	[if exp='game.party.members.count == 6']
