Despite the fact that the women are required to do something unreasonably harsh, they say they are willing to do so in order to protect their friends.[k]
I was moved by everyone's feelings. They care about their friends. They're passionate about justice... I can't help but feel proud to be able to fight alongside them.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
...Earlier, Blue said that another woman would be fine.[k]
If I don't neglect that, I might be able to protect everyone in the party. There's no guarantee, but we don't have to sacrifice everyone unconditionally.[k]
...Right now, it wouldn't be surprising if everyone were slaughtered by Murmur at any moment.[k]
So I can't let Blue get away. Right now, I have to get this guy on our side. I can always reconsider later.[k]
